arked=3D"1" tabindex=3D"-1"></a> Set Up the Payflow Gateway Testing Environ=
ment</h2><p>Before testing transactions be sure you are linked to the test =
servers.</p><p>Direct all transactions to the host URL for testing. See
<a href=3D"https://developer.paypal.com/api/nvp-soap/payflow/integration-gu=
